*Hugo Hovenkamp withdrew from the squad before the tournament began,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nhnieuws.nl/nieuws/246679/hugo-hovenkamp-het-winnen-van-de-beker-gaf-een-gevoel-van-onoverwinnelijkheid|title=Hugo Hovenkamp: "Het winnen van de beker gaf een gevoel van onoverwinnelijkheid"|website=nhnieuws.nl|language=nl|date=29 May 2019|access-date=17 January 2019}}</ref> but after the deadline for naming replacement players had passed. The Netherlands thus went to the World Cup with only 21 players.

